PN,42301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FA leading Post Office Horizon scandal
OL,8,Fcampaigner has said the Government
OL,9,Fcannot label its soon-to-close
OL,10,Fcompensation scheme a success as some
OL,11,Fvictims are still awaiting "full and
OL,12,Ffair redress".
OL,26,@sD@\OUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FChristopher Head, who became the
OL,8,Fyoungest subpostmaster at the age of
OL,9,F18 when he took over the West Bolden
OL,10,Fbranch near Sunderland in 2006, said
OL,11,Fthe group litigation order (GLO)
OL,12,Fscheme could have "wrapped up a year
OL,13,Fago" if the Department for Business
OL,14,Fand Trade (DBT) had listened to
OL,15,Ffeedback from claimants.
OL,17,FThe GLO scheme was set up following
OL,18,Fthe high-profile legal action launched
OL,19,Fby Sir Alan Bates and 554 others
OL,20,Fagainst the Post Office in the High
OL,21,FCourt between 2017 and 2019.
OL,26,@tD@SOUuD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FA total of 492 subpostmasters have
OL,8,Fbeen entitled to apply for redress
OL,9,Funder the scheme, with the remaining
OL,10,F63 told to apply through a different
OL,11,Fprocess because of their wrongful
OL,12,Fcriminal convictions.
OL,14,FThe Horizon accounting system, run by
OL,15,FJapanese firm Fujitsu, made it look
OL,16,Flike money was missing from
OL,17,Fsubpostmasters' branch accounts.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FIt is at the centre of the long-
OL,8,Frunning Post Office scandal, which saw
OL,9,Faround 1,000 people wrongly prosecuted
OL,10,Fand convicted throughout the UK
OL,11,Fbetween 1999 and 2015.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday (21 April), DBT said the
OL,14,FGLO scheme would close to new
OL,15,Fapplicants on 31 July, with a view to
OL,16,Fconcluding on 31 December following
OL,17,F"successful delivery".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FFollowing the announcement, Mr Head
OL,8,Ftold the Press Association: "That's
OL,9,Fthe department saying it's been
OL,10,Fsuccessful, and that to me comes back
OL,11,Fto a fundamental problem we've had
OL,12,Fwith Post Office and DBT all the time,
OL,13,Fwhich is that they are marking their
OL,14,Fown homework.
OL,16,F"They're going to say 'we've received
OL,17,Fthis many claims and we've paid them
OL,18,Fso that means it's been successful',
OL,19,Fbut what I call successful is... has
OL,20,Fthe scheme successfully paid full and
OL,21,Ffair redress to those people?
OL,26,@pD@]OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,F"The department class full and fair
OL,8,Fredress being paid when someone
OL,9,Faccepts an offer ` but there might be
OL,10,Fvarious reasons why someone might
OL,11,Faccept an offer.
OL,13,F"So I don't see why it should be DBT
OL,14,Fthat should say that it has been
OL,15,Fsuccessful, it should be the claimants.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,F"I would honestly like every single
OL,8,Fperson to be asked the question 'do
OL,9,Fyou believe you have received redress
OL,10,Fthat is full and fair?' and just place
OL,11,Fit in a yes and no table ` that will
OL,12,Ftell you whether the scheme has been
OL,13,Fsuccessful.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,F"In my view, in some cases it has been
OL,8,Fsuccessful because we have seen
OL,9,Fdeliveries of redress that are above
OL,10,Fwhat people have claimed, but there
OL,11,Fare other people I know who have said
OL,12,F'I've had enough, I've literally had
OL,13,Fenough', and therefore the scheme
OL,14,Fmight have been completed, rather than
OL,15,Fsuccessful.
OL,17,F"But there is still a number of people
OL,18,Fwho have not received what the
OL,19,Fdepartment set out to achieve, which
OL,20,Fis full and fair redress."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FMr Head was falsely accused of
OL,8,Fstealing more than #80,000 from his
OL,9,Fbranch before the criminal case
OL,10,Fagainst him was dropped, at which
OL,11,Fpoint he was pursued by the Post
OL,12,FOffice through the civil courts.
OL,14,FAddressing the GLO scheme, he told PA:
OL,15,F"My view of it is that the scheme as a
OL,16,Fwhole, if you want to look at it from
OL,17,Fthe vast majority of cases, is doing
OL,18,Fwhat it was designed to do ` problem
OL,19,Fis, it's taken a hell of a long time
OL,20,Fto get the scheme in the position that
OL,21,Fit is now."
OL,26,@wD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FMr Head said his claim took the
OL,8,Flongest to be settled, spanning a
OL,9,Ftotal of 744 days after he felt forced
OL,10,Fto "sit on" his claim to avoid
OL,11,Fpotentially losing money by taking his
OL,12,Fcase to an appeal.
OL,14,FHe could eventually proceed with his
OL,15,Fclaim after the scheme was changed to
OL,16,Fincorporate a "best offer" policy, in
OL,17,Fcase an independent panel said their
OL,18,Fclaim was worth less than what DBT had
OL,19,Foffered.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@KO]xD@OOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FMr Head said he was representing
OL,8,Fvulnerable people in "seriously ill
OL,9,Fhealth" who are part of the GLO
OL,10,Fscheme, who have not been able to
OL,11,Fcommunicate with their own lawyers
OL,12,Fbecause they do not "understand the
OL,13,Flegalities", or are in the "right
OL,14,Fframe of mind".
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@GO]tD@UOUuD@KO]uD@\OUvD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FHe said DBT had taken too long to get
OL,8,Fthe scheme where it is today, saying:
OL,9,F"You're providing them feedback and
OL,10,Fsaying 'these problems are happening',
OL,11,Fand the department's stance in the
OL,12,Fmost part that I could see, especially
OL,13,Fin the very first 12-18 months of the
OL,14,Fscheme operating... they just buried
OL,15,Ftheir heads in the sand.
OL,17,F"There was always an excuse about why
OL,18,Fit couldn't be done.
OL,26,@qD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,F"If the department had actually taken
OL,8,Fon the feedback and actually listened
OL,9,Fto the claimants and their lawyers
OL,10,Fabout what things could have been done
OL,11,Fto improve or implement it, we could
OL,12,Fhave had this scheme wrapped up a year
OL,13,Fago.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,F"The fact that they dug their heels
OL,8,Fin... I think the gripe is the delay
OL,9,Fdoing it and the department's refusal
OL,10,Fto listen to claimants and their
OL,11,Flawyers was the first part ` and there
OL,12,Fare still people who still believe
OL,13,Fthey haven't received the full and
OL,14,Ffair redress they are entitled to.
OL,16,F"But it's very hard to say whether
OL,17,Fthat's the department's fault or
OL,18,Fsomething wrong with the claim."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FDBT said as of March 31, 90% of GLO
OL,8,Fscheme claimants had received final
OL,9,Fredress, with #223 million paid out to
OL,10,Fvictims.
OL,12,FPost Office Minister Blair McDougall
OL,13,Fsaid: "The postmasters in the GLO
OL,14,Fgroup were the first to lead the
OL,15,Fcharge for justice, and they deserve
OL,16,Fto see this chapter closed with the
OL,17,Ffull and fair redress they are owed.
OL,19,F"Setting these deadlines is about
OL,20,Fmaking sure that happens.
OL,26,@uD@GOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776856004
OL,3,CHorizon redress scheme 'not a success'
OL,4,Cuntil all victims get full and fair
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,F"We are 90% of the way there, and I am
OL,8,Fdetermined that the remaining claims
OL,9,Fare resolved quickly and fairly, with
OL,10,Fproper support for anyone who needs
OL,11,Fit."
OL,13,FDBT said more than #1.5 billion had
OL,14,Fbeen paid out to Horizon victims since
OL,15,Fthe summer of 2024.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G16/17
